00:06:06.799 --> 00:06:08.734
- Mm-hmm.
- I'm going to the bathroom

00:06:08.767 --> 00:06:10.469
over 30 times a day.
- Mm-hmm.

00:06:10.502 --> 00:06:12.471
- And I'm just, like,
"Something's not right."

00:06:12.504 --> 00:06:14.073
