00:06:14.106 --> 00:06:16.308
But I'm very energetic.

00:06:16.341 --> 00:06:18.077
I'm an on-the-go type of person,

00:06:18.110 --> 00:06:20.513
and I'm starting
to feel sluggish

00:06:20.546 --> 00:06:22.782
all these different days.

00:06:22.815 --> 00:06:23.983
And I felt myself
leaving my body.

00:06:24.016 --> 00:06:25.351
- I see.

00:06:25.384 --> 00:06:29.021
- One of my cousins
rushed me to the hospital,

00:06:29.054 --> 00:06:31.090
and they checked my levels,

00:06:31.123 --> 00:06:33.092
