but I'm going to tell you,

00:07:41.193 --> 00:07:42.895
you don't want to put
any weight on it.

00:07:42.928 --> 00:07:44.163
- Yeah, I'm fighting it.

00:07:44.196 --> 00:07:46.232
- Who's your regular doctor?

00:07:46.265 --> 00:07:48.133
- I don't have one.

00:07:48.166 --> 00:07:49.969
Uh-huh.

00:07:52.938 --> 00:07:53.973
- Okay.

00:07:56.642 --> 00:07:58.944
So, what I was going to suggest

00:07:58.977 --> 00:08:01.180
