00:36:13.604 --> 00:36:15.906 line:0%
And it's, like, "Wait a second.

00:36:15.939 --> 00:36:19.343 line:0%
You're getting it wrong,
because we do have food."

00:36:19.376 --> 00:36:21.412 line:0%
What we don't have
