to unlimited calories,

00:36:40.330 --> 00:36:41.799
but we still have
those ancient cravings.

00:36:41.832 --> 00:36:46.203
We've created foods
that are processed.

00:36:46.236 --> 00:36:47.871
We remove the fiber,

00:36:47.904 --> 00:36:50.140
