01:24:29.163 --> 01:24:31.933
HURLEY: When I developed
type 1 diabetes in 1975,

01:24:31.966 --> 01:24:36.604 line:0%
there was no such thing
as doing a finger-prick test

01:24:36.637 --> 01:24:40.908
to find out
what your blood sugar was.

01:24:40.941 --> 01:24:42.210 line:0%
