01:24:42.243 --> 01:24:47.815 line:0%
when, in the early '80s,
this became available.

01:24:47.848 --> 01:24:51.619 line:0%
People could get a little drop
of blood,

01:24:51.652 --> 01:24:53.554 line:0%
put it on a little strip,

01:24:53.587 --> 01:24:58.860 line:0%
and voilà, there is
your sugar level.

01:24:58.893 --> 01:25:01.629 line:0%
This was a huge breakthrough.

01:25:01.662 --> 01:25:05.032 line:0%
Then the insulin pumps,
soon after.

01:25:05.065 --> 01:25:07.168
