01:25:09.136 --> 01:25:13.441
Yes, but the pump
allows you to release,

01:25:13.474 --> 01:25:17.812
like your body does,
a little bit every few minutes.

01:25:17.845 --> 01:25:21.682
And it gives you just
what you need as you need it.

01:25:21.715 --> 01:25:23.651
NICOLE:
