01:25:23.684 --> 01:25:25.786
and then it also comes
with a needle.

01:25:25.819 --> 01:25:31.092
NICOLE: I've been on an insulin
pump for 16 years.

01:25:31.125 --> 01:25:34.428
You turn it around,

01:25:34.461 --> 01:25:36.230
and I am going to fill it
with insulin.

01:25:36.263 --> 01:25:38.866 line:0%
So this is what
the insulin comes out of.

01:25:38.899 --> 01:25:42.370 line:0%
A needle does go into my skin,
but then it retracts,

01:25:42.403 --> 01:25:45.006 line:0%
