01:27:00.114 --> 01:27:03.718
These things keep me alive.

01:27:03.751 --> 01:27:05.853
The next step for diabetes

01:27:05.886 --> 01:27:11.592
is, is connecting this monitor
with my pump,

01:27:11.625 --> 01:27:14.161
so that the two talk
to each other,

01:27:14.194 --> 01:27:21.602
