and then they said,

01:37:48.528 --> 01:37:49.830
"Well, we are going to push it
to 4:00 a.m."

01:37:49.863 --> 01:37:52.399
So I was, like, "Okay."

01:37:52.432 --> 01:37:54.801
People are calling me,
people are texting.

01:37:54.834 --> 01:37:56.737
Like, this was happening.

